wer plant in illinois ·      the mw liberty gasfired power plant in pennsylvania ·      the mw richland gasfired power plant in ohio ·      the mw stryker oilfired power plant in ohio   dynegy’s other acquisition of duke energy nyse duk’s commercial generation and retail assets in the midwest has received all approvals and is expected to close on april  subscribe to the power engineering enewsletter sponsored content is made possible by our sponsor it does not necessarily reflect the views of our editorial staff related articles nv energy issues rfp for  mw of renewables or cogeneration bids are due july    bolze out stokes in as head of ge power bolze flannery finance chief jeff bornstein and oil and gas chief lorenzo simonelli were all in the running to succeed immelt by  and submitted their plans for running the company industry jobs senior energy specialists energy innovation program consultant  sme director of creative technical solutions principal engineer – distribution pc more industry jobs featured whitepaper optimizing power plant size with reciprocating internal combustion engines new metering solution controls condensate in hrsg systems how transcanada cultivated confidence in risk analysis with deltek acumen more whitepapers webcasts delivering digitalisation exploring the potential for the power sector generationhub quarterly market update december  speakers kent knutson barry cassell wayne barber importance of used oil analysis in optimising gas engine output speakers frank heber derek selby kelvin ross transmissionhub quarterly market update november  speakers kent knutson more webcasts products showcase caterpillar introduces new gas generator set for continuous applications the cat g is targeted for flexible applications using a single unit for both standby and load management operations ge provides turbine financing for pennsylvania combinedcycle plant the deal for the plant expected to produce  mw upon commercial operation in  also includes finan